                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 811.3335/33</note>
                <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Embassy</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Buenos Aires</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1917-07-31T16:00:00-04:16">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 31, 1917, 4 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Ships sailed this morning. Admiral and I waited to make parting call on President
                    who expressed best wishes for good fortune of the squadron. Admiral has left to
                    rejoin fleet on Argentine cruiser.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Stimson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
